            <h3 class="mt-1 text-lg font-black text-slate-950">@TransferTarget?.UrunAdi</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600">Merkez: @TransferTarget?.MerkezStok · Bu bayi: @TransferTarget?.BayiStok</p>
